Miri,Device,Description,is,a,mobile,device,description,service,that,returns,information,and,descriptions,about,mobile,devices,using,OpenDdr,resources,The,Miri,Device,Description,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Miri,with,other,applications,The,main,API,method,is,returning,information,on,the,mobile,device